00:47:03.770 --> 00:47:07.900
going to say four electron volts
strikes a gold surface,

00:47:07.900 --> 00:47:11.015
and here we're saying that the
gold surface has a work

00:47:11.015 --> 00:47:15.990
function of 5.1 electron volts,
what is the maximum

00:47:15.990 --> 00:47:31.490
